### ============================================
### Flight Service API (Port 8080)
### ============================================
### 항공편 검색 및 좌석 관리


### ------------------------------------------
### 항공편 검색
### ------------------------------------------

### 항공편 검색 (서울 -> 제주)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/flights?from=ICN&to=CJU&date=2024-12-25
Accept: application/json

###

### 항공편 검색 (서울 -> 부산)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/flights?from=ICN&to=PUS&date=2024-12-25
Accept: application/json


### ------------------------------------------
### 좌석 가용성 확인
### ------------------------------------------

### KE001 항공편 좌석 가용성 확인
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/flights/KE001/availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seatClass": "ECONOMY",
  "passengerCount": 2
}

###

### OZ456 항공편 좌석 가용성 확인
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/flights/OZ456/availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seatClass": "BUSINESS",
  "passengerCount": 1
}


### ------------------------------------------
### 좌석 예약
### ------------------------------------------

### KE001 항공편 좌석 예약
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/flights/KE001/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passengerName": "Hong Gildong",
  "seatClass": "ECONOMY",
  "seatNumber": "23A"
}

###

### 좌석 예약 취소
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/flights/KE001/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": "RES-001",
  "seatNumber": "23A"
}
